data.description: Welcome to Goose Creek Landing! This Castle Rock built home awaits you! The first floor open concept floor plan makes this home easy for those family and friend get togethers. This home features 4 bedrooms, with the primary on the first floor, and all others on the second floor. Built in 2020 and new vinyl plank floors installed 4/6/23 this home needs nothing but for you to move in. The 2 1/2 car garage is perfect for the car enthusiast, wood worker, in the household making it easy to park and still have an area for your tools and equipment without them being in the way. A transfer switch for a 50amp generator has been professionally installed. COME SEE IT FOR YOURSELF!
